<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>文献阅读 - Tag - LoveIt</title><link>https://zyqi17.github.io/tags/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/</link><description>文献阅读 - Tag - LoveIt</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><copyright>This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://zyqi17.github.io/tags/%E6%96%87%E7%8C%AE%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>刘小磊博士论文</title><link>https://zyqi17.github.io/farmcpu/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>zyqi</author><guid>https://zyqi17.github.io/farmcpu/</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>本文阐述了一个新的算法来解决混合线性模型中存在的混杂问题 (<a href="zotero://open-pdf/library/items/D7L9J2UW?page=7&amp;annotation=QRJE7Y3I" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">pdf</a>)</p>
<p>混合线性模型带来了假阴性 (<a href="zotero://open-pdf/library/items/D7L9J2UW?page=10&amp;annotation=WB4HYPZ2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">pdf</a>)</p>
<p>最有效的去消除这种假阳性的策略是将群体背景作为固定效应，亲缘关系矩阵作为随机效应加在一个混合线性模型中 (<a href="zotero://open-pdf/library/items/D7L9J2UW?page=11&amp;annotation=N972RUGJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">pdf</a>)</p>
<p><strong>对于与群体结构相关联的复杂性状，Q+K模型虽然可以很好的控制假阳性，但同时大大降低了模型对候选基因信号的检测强度</strong>。随后，各种各样的策略被用于改进混合线性模型的检测效力。 (<a href="zotero://open-pdf/library/items/D7L9J2UW?page=13&amp;annotation=6FS38JZ6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">pdf</a>)</p>
<p>随机选取了数据中10%的位点用 GAPIT 软件(Lipka et al. 2012)构建亲缘关系矩阵和计算主成分。 (<a href="zotero://open-pdf/library/items/D7L9J2UW?page=20&amp;annotation=X2938XMT" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">pdf</a>)</p>
<p>Genome-wide association study of 107 phenotypes in Arabidopsis thaliana inbred lines (<a href="zotero://open-pdf/library/items/D7L9J2UW?page=65&amp;annotation=PNINL929" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">pdf</a>)</p>
<p>当一个关联位点本身或者其附近上下游一定距离内（例如，50,000碱基对）的遗传标记被检测到时，认定为该关联位点被成功检测。 (<a href="zotero://open-pdf/library/items/D7L9J2UW?page=23&amp;annotation=VLK7JXPJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreffer ">pdf</a>)</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>